        "mainbody": "'''Scottie Torilson''' was the leader of the [[Sons of Light]], a knighthood devoted to [[Torm]] in the early 8{{th}} century [[DR]]. He fought with them during the latter days of the [[Weeping War]]. He died in the {{YearlinkName|713}}, while defending a strategically unimportant [[Elf|elven]] village, because his duty demanded it. He was the possessor of the one true [[enchanted]] [[longsword]] ''[[Daystar]]''."
